  "messages": [
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Just got a call from a recruiter, but it's not in compliance. Feeling like I'm being typecast.",
    "time": "2026-05-04T10:47:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Hey, just a heads up, I had a few job interviews today. Nothing concrete yet, but I'm hopeful. How was your day?",
    "time": "2026-05-04T20:08:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel 'Danny' Okafor",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "You won't believe what I found in the MH_Timeline_Master doc. It's getting worse. Need to talk soon.",
    "time": "2026-05-05T15:34:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Reema Chatterjee",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Hi Reema, I've been following your work on healthcare corruption. I think I might have a story that could interest you. Would love to discuss further.",
    "time": "2026-05-06T12:47:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Did you manage to get those legal-hold notices? I really need something concrete to move forward.",
    "time": "2026-05-07T11:11:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Severance package is looking thinner than I thought. Starting to get worried about our financials. We should talk about budgeting tonight.",
    "time": "2026-05-08T14:25:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Daniel 'Danny' Okafor",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "I'm telling you, Danny, this leak is going to be huge. I just need to get it to the right people. You think I should reach out to more reporters?",
    "time": "2026-05-09T15:26:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Reema Chatterjee",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Following up on my previous email. I've got some new information that I think could be relevant to your investigation. Would appreciate the chance to discuss.",
    "time": "2026-05-10T12:32:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just reviewed the latest HIPAA logs. The gaps are still there. When can we discuss further?",
    "time": "2026-05-11T11:47:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hey, have you thought more about reaching out to Reema Chatterjee at the WSJ? I think it's our best bet.",
    "time": "2026-05-12T10:43:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "The deadline for the whistleblower submission is approaching. Do you have any updates on the documents you mentioned?",
    "time": "2026-05-13T11:34:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "I've managed to get my hands on some internal memos that might be useful. I'll send them over once I've redacted them.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T10:47:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've been thinking, maybe we should create a secure drop for the documents instead of sending them directly to the journalist.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T11:01:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hope you're doing well. My family is having a get-together this weekend. Wish I could invite you, but you know how it is.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T11:35:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Megan's been on my case about getting a new job. I don't know how much longer I can keep this up without telling her everything.",
    "time": "2026-05-17T11:16:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just reviewed the documents. I think we have a strong case for the whistleblower report.",
    "time": "2026-05-18T10:47:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey, just wanted to update you on my job search. Nothing yet, but I'm still working on the whistleblower report.",
    "time": "2026-05-18T20:08:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've made some progress on the document collection. Should have everything ready soon.",
    "time": "2026-05-19T11:49:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just a quick update on my day. Nothing new to report.",
    "time": "2026-05-19T20:57:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I'm thinking of submitting the report to the WSJ. What do you think?",
    "time": "2026-05-20T10:11:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I'm getting close to submitting the report. Just need to finalize a few things.",
    "time": "2026-05-20T19:45:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've been in touch with a journalist who's interested in the story. Should I move forward?",
    "time": "2026-05-21T12:06:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just checking in. How was your day?",
    "time": "2026-05-21T20:02:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "The deadline for submission is approaching. I need to finalize everything ASAP.",
    "time": "2026-05-22T10:30:09"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "The deadline is getting close. I'm feeling the pressure to get everything just right.",
    "time": "2026-05-22T18:42:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've finalized the report and I'm ready to submit. Just need to confirm a few details.",
    "time": "2026-05-23T11:42:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I'm almost done with the report. Just a few more hours of work.",
    "time": "2026-05-23T20:56:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've submitted the report. Now we just have to wait and see what happens.",
    "time": "2026-05-24T10:52:24"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "It's done. The report is submitted and I'm waiting to hear back.",
    "time": "2026-05-24T19:02:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Let's discuss the whistleblower planning and next steps. I've been thinking about reaching out to the WSJ reporter.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T10:47:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey, just confirming our call schedule for this week. Want to make sure we're on the same page.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T21:38:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "I've sent over some documents and information that might be helpful for our case. Let me know what you think.",
    "time": "2026-05-26T11:44:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just wanted to update you on the job search and whistleblower planning. Nothing new to report yet, but I'm still working on it.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T12:52:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just got some new information from M. Calderón. Want to discuss the latest developments and get your thoughts.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T11:36:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "What's the plan for family dinner tonight? Should I pick up anything on my way home?",
    "time": "2026-05-29T15:45:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Just wanted to offer some advice and support. You're doing the right thing, even if it's tough. Keep pushing forward.",
    "time": "2026-05-30T11:41:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Megan Doyle-Reinhardt",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just wanted to update you again on the job search and whistleblower planning. I know it's been a tough week, but I'm still working on it.",
    "time": "2026-05-31T12:32:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "M. Calderón",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just got a call from a recruiter about a new compliance role. Thinking about how this could impact our timeline. Want to discuss tonight?",
    "time": "2026-06-01T10:47:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Reema Chatterjee",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Subject: Confidential Source - MeridianHealth HIPAA Logging Gaps. Dear Reema, I hope this email finds you well. I am reaching out as a former Senior Compliance Analyst at MeridianHealth Solutions with information about systemic HIPAA logging gaps that I believe are of public interest. I would like to discuss this further with you and explore the possibility of sharing my story with the Wall Street Journal.",
    "time": "2026-06-01T22:33:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Danny Okafor",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hey man, just saw the news about MeridianHealth's latest 'realignment'. You think this is related to your situation? We should catch up soon, maybe over a call this weekend?",
    "time": "2026-06-02T13:49:54"
   }
